  "description": "<h3>Back of Case - Nintendo DS (US) (from <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/story-of-noahs-ark/adblurbs\">Ad Blurbs</a>)</h3><h3>Read the delightful story of “Noah’s Ark” translated into a fun and interactive storybook form. Or listen to the narration like an audio book.</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Learn to spell the names of the animals living on the Ark.</li>\n<li>Perform in an animal orchestra and create your own music by playing notes on the teeth of a happy hippopotamus!</li>\n<li>Practice your penmanship by using the Nintendo DC stylus to trace letters.</li>\n<li>Color in charming pictures of Noah’s animals to create your own pieces of art.</li>\n<li>Play a variety of mini-games to help Noah build the Ark, gather the animals in pairs, and steer the Ark to safety.</li>\n</ul>",
